{"tid":1309655,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭「非法處理屍體罪」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-07-12T09:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T15:03:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"427f885593b284af12e973b41c8357ebffcc558f","tid":1309655,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:56:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190712/20726415\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190712%2F20726415&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUygcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=29ecacfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190712%2F20726415&h=f3e1fa40\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190712/20726415</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭「非法處理屍體罪」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190712/large/e8804a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190712%2Flarge%2Fe8804a.jpg&h=c1740fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《The Autopsy of Jane Doe》劇照(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n林鄭的「壽終正寢」論，果然又因其剛愎自用語言偽術，再陷自己於政治深淵、誠信危機，怎麼爬上來？<br />\n<br />\n本來簡單一句永久「撤回」惡法，撤銷「暴動」大搜捕及獨立調查，港人的怨憤或可平復一點──但她選擇繼續火上加油，希望示威遊行抗爭可以十八區遍地開花，才是「宏願」。<br />\n<br />\n即使有人認為林鄭是傀儡特首只能照稿讀，但其偏執型人格障礙亦令事件僵化。「你哋叫我撤回就撤回，咁咪好冇面？」──正如「你哋話鬍鬚曾派6千蚊人人有份快靚正，叫我照派就照派，咁咪好冇面？」<br />\n<br />\n一己之私，賣港殃民。各國各界特別是專業人士，認為「壽終正寢」並非法律用語，並且不夠正式、嚴肅。只是個晦氣於扮斬釘截鐵的「擬人法」修辭。<br />\n<br />\n我不是法律界人士，但既然「擬人」，壽終正寢定有屍體了，為免借屍還魂、死剩把口、鹹魚翻生、變成殭屍──那惡法仍可重來招禍，屍體一定要埋葬入土為安，或火化成灰，才一了百了，林鄭如何處理？<br />\n<br />\n要知，「處理屍體不當」，又即「阻止屍體合法埋葬」是違法的，此罪那涉嫌在台謀殺港女的陳同佳亦同時干犯。林鄭初心利用「為潘女雪冤」來強推惡法，現完全失敗了，亦應送犯至台「彰顯公義」，何以自己又犯同罪？  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n政府收風 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n有兩手 (尊子)"},{"pid":"944c304d8d94f4480d80910f2e30a2dc8b45dd54","tid":1309655,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"畀張圖嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c598e8d6f6eb80d8107f7cb427dd1dce9e6c34","tid":1309655,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:07:38.000Z","msg":"20190712 大埔連儂隧道現場  live<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t9arACvUqPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dt9arACvUqPI&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUygcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=559cdc82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t9arACvUqPI</a>"},{"pid":"ea1e3c9a46ab8dfa9b818c8ad42831d7b242870c","tid":1309655,"uid":267342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:02:38.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936a24d8ea47b09eec7d02a2f8cf0d6f68a8ff02","tid":1309655,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"七 月 十 三 ！光 復 上 水 ！踢 走 水 貨 客！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310098\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310098</a><br />\n<br />\n【推上熱門】713光復上水資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309441\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309441</a><br />\n<br />\n[714/721] 野餐及夢遊服飾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309156\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309156</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中火力推Post</span></span>"}]}